OL,3,COldham mountaineer taking on Everest
OL,4,Cfor second time after setting record
OL,6,FA mountaineer from Oldham aiming to
OL,7,Fclimb the 14 highest peaks in the
OL,8,Fworld - is ready to face Mount Everest
OL,9,Ffor a second time as he raises money
OL,10,Ffor charity.
OL,12,FAkke Rahman, 41, said he is starting
OL,13,Fthe challenge by beginning the climb
OL,14,Fup Mount Everest this month, having
OL,15,Fbecome the first British Muslim to
OL,16,Fclimb the world's highest mountain in
OL,17,F2022.
OL,19,FHe said: "I'm ready to face it. I'm
OL,20,Fdoing it for humanity and I'm helping
OL,21,Fpeople."
