OL,3,COldham mountaineer taking on Everest
OL,4,Cfor second time after setting record
OL,6,F"Last time I did it, I did it in 21
OL,7,Fdays, which was pretty much half the
OL,8,Fexpected time, so I'm hoping some of
OL,9,Fthat experience will get me through
OL,10,Fthis."
OL,12,FThe 14 mountains he will be climbing
OL,13,Fare all over 8,000 metres tall and he
OL,14,Fexpects to complete his mission around
OL,15,FSeptember 2025.
OL,17,FHe will be taking on the challenge in
OL,18,Ffour phases, with the first phase
OL,19,Fcomprising Everest, Lhotse, Makalu and
OL,20,FKanchenjunga.
