OL,3,COldham mountaineer taking on Everest
OL,4,Cfor second time after setting record
OL,6,FThe mountaineer, based in Oldham,
OL,7,FGreater Manchester, said: "I feel
OL,8,Fconfident. I'm going to go there, give
OL,9,Fit my best shot, and I'm going to take
OL,10,Fthem one by one and that's probably
OL,11,Fthe best way to do it."
OL,13,FK2, Cho Oyu and Shishapangma are among
OL,14,Fthe other mountains Mr Rahman will be
OL,15,Fclimbing.
