OL,4,Cfor second time after setting record
OL,6,FOn preparing for the challenge, he
OL,7,Fsaid: "The thing is, we don't have
OL,8,Fhigh altitude mountains in the UK, so
OL,9,FI can't really go and get myself
OL,10,Facclimated, so what I do is just
OL,11,Ffitness.
OL,13,F" I run five or six times a week, and
OL,14,FI go to the gym and I do some light
OL,15,Fworkouts just to build my strength."
OL,17,FHe will be documenting his journey on
OL,18,Fhis Instagram,
