OL,3,COldham mountaineer taking on Everest
OL,4,Cfor second time after setting record
OL,6,FHe started out in climbing by scaling
OL,7,FMount Snowdon in Wales in 2019, vowing
OL,8,Fthat if he enjoyed it he would go on
OL,9,Fto tackle Elbrus, Europe's tallest
OL,10,Fmountain, in Russia.
OL,12,FIn 2020, Mr Rahman climbed Mount
OL,13,FKilimanjaro and Mont Blanc within a
OL,14,Fweek and later that year, he broke the
OL,15,FUK record for climbing Elbrus after
OL,16,Freaching the summit in less than 24
OL,17,Fhours.
