OL,4,Cfor second time after setting record
OL,6,FMr Rahman said: "I took up
OL,7,Fmountaineering just to inspire my
OL,8,Fchildren and show them that you can do
OL,9,Fmore than just average and you can do
OL,10,Fgreat things."
OL,12,FI just wanted to be an inspiration to
OL,13,Fthem and at least they can say, 'my
OL,14,Fdad was this and I aspire to be
OL,15,Fsomething like this or something
OL,16,Fbetter'."
