OL,6,FThat's where it all started and then
OL,7,Fit just sort of spiralled out of
OL,8,Fcontrol."As a brand ambassador for UK
OL,9,FIslamic Mission, Mr Rahman will be
OL,10,Fraising money for the charity to help
OL,11,Fcommunities in Bangladesh, the UK and
OL,12,Felsewhere.
OL,14,FHe is motivated to inspire other
OL,15,Fpeople to get fit while raising money
OL,16,Ffor causes close to his heart.
OL,18,FHe said: "Mountaineering is my passion
OL,19,Fbut my fuel is helping people."I'm
OL,20,Fdoing my best for humanity to try and
OL,21,Fhelp as many people as I can."
